WEBVTT

01:52.250 --> 01:57.340
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.729 --> 02:01.900
[Episode 6]

02:14.630 --> 02:15.630
Master.

02:17.550 --> 02:19.510
Go invite him in.

02:19.630 --> 02:20.630
Yes.

02:36.350 --> 02:38.820
[Linglong Tower]

04:52.190 --> 04:53.070
Lord Zheng.

04:54.050 --> 04:55.130
If that's the case,

04:55.159 --> 04:58.020
there is no point
in continuing this conversation.

04:58.980 --> 05:00.580
You've got the wrong person.

05:04.800 --> 05:06.720
Second Young Master Qi.

05:07.720 --> 05:09.450
I am not Second Young Master Qi.

05:10.240 --> 05:11.600
My name is Gao Ran,

05:11.880 --> 05:13.930
and I serve Qi Zheng.

05:14.400 --> 05:16.130
The Governor of the Nine Cities

05:16.430 --> 05:17.780
will only be him.

05:22.310 --> 05:23.430
For a subject,

05:25.050 --> 05:26.350
loyalty is enough.

05:27.800 --> 05:28.660
For the people,

05:29.360 --> 05:31.020
a wise governor is paramount.

05:32.040 --> 05:33.970
A peach tree grows by the open well;

05:36.000 --> 05:39.280
a plum tree stands beside it.

05:40.090 --> 05:43.140
When insects come to bite the peach roots,

05:45.050 --> 05:49.409
the plum tree dies in its place.

05:57.159 --> 05:59.390
Trees sacrifice for each other,

06:00.120 --> 06:02.550
yet brothers forget one another.

06:04.530 --> 06:07.870
I once taught you this poem.

06:08.490 --> 06:09.870
Do you still remember?

06:15.510 --> 06:17.910
The plum tree used
to die for the peach tree.

06:18.960 --> 06:19.980
But now,

06:20.540 --> 06:22.340
what if the plum tree dies?

06:25.920 --> 06:27.300
The peach tree

06:27.860 --> 06:29.540
can live in its stead

06:30.560 --> 06:31.950
and thrive for it.

06:39.850 --> 06:42.080
Peach and plum trees share the same roots;

06:42.080 --> 06:43.610
they live and die together.

06:44.870 --> 06:45.750
Furthermore,

06:46.350 --> 06:48.280
the fertile land of the Nine Cities

06:48.750 --> 06:51.010
is enough to nourish thousands of trees.

06:52.190 --> 06:54.120
How can such insignificant tricks

06:54.350 --> 06:56.480
stop the vast power of heaven?

06:58.720 --> 07:00.930
It seems you are prepared.

07:06.770 --> 07:07.570
Lord Zheng,

07:08.360 --> 07:09.730
Qi Zheng is actually

07:10.280 --> 07:12.100
the wise governor.

08:31.430 --> 08:32.120
Stop!

08:35.640 --> 08:36.700
Put the blade down.

08:40.570 --> 08:42.299
I told you to put the blade down!

09:05.470 --> 09:06.510
Are you crazy?

09:06.780 --> 09:08.710
Killing your own woman?

09:09.040 --> 09:10.700
The footsteps sounded wrong.

09:10.860 --> 09:12.260
Fan Yun isn't that heavy.

09:12.600 --> 09:13.300
Speak!

09:13.990 --> 09:15.140
Where is Fan Yun?

10:42.030 --> 10:43.000
Fan Yun.

10:44.100 --> 10:45.810
Fan Yun, are you okay?

10:45.880 --> 10:46.760
Qi Zheng,

10:46.910 --> 10:48.300
thank goodness you're finally here.

10:48.300 --> 10:50.160
I thought I'd never see you again.

10:51.910 --> 10:53.000
I'll get you out of here.

10:53.000 --> 10:54.080
Okay.

11:00.890 --> 11:02.250
Watch out, Qi Zheng!

11:08.640 --> 11:09.560
Hang in there.

11:29.870 --> 11:31.460
♪ Spring winds, autumn rain ♪

11:31.330 --> 11:32.240
Fan Yun,

11:31.480 --> 11:32.960
♪ Flowers bloom for a single season ♪

11:32.980 --> 11:34.980
♪ Fallen petals turn into mud ♪

11:33.390 --> 11:34.550
I'm a man of my word.

11:35.010 --> 11:37.460
♪ It's never ♪

11:35.480 --> 11:37.280
I will definitely take you back.

11:37.480 --> 11:40.620
♪ The ending I crave ♪

11:41.700 --> 11:43.900
♪ I'd be the wick lit up ♪

11:43.980 --> 11:45.700
♪ For you each night ♪

11:45.800 --> 11:47.740
♪ Burning myself bright ♪

11:47.770 --> 11:50.360
♪ Beside you as you hold the brush ♪

11:50.390 --> 11:53.210
♪ Till every streak of ink fades away ♪

11:54.870 --> 11:56.960
♪ I search and search through all days ♪

11:56.980 --> 11:58.210
♪ Lingering on with unwilling heart ♪

11:58.230 --> 12:00.310
♪ What does a final choice matter? ♪

12:00.340 --> 12:02.840
♪ In the moment of looking back ♪

12:02.860 --> 12:05.840
♪ This life is worth it ♪

12:06.530 --> 12:09.200
♪ When no dawn can be seen ahead ♪

12:09.230 --> 12:13.070
♪ Who are the dream-walkers? ♪

12:13.270 --> 12:15.270
♪ Facing the light ♪

12:15.290 --> 12:19.040
♪ Singing a long song along the way ♪

12:16.360 --> 12:17.390
Kill.

12:19.210 --> 12:21.820
♪ Tear the dark night apart ♪

12:21.840 --> 12:23.520
♪ Turn my whole heart ♪

12:23.550 --> 12:25.550
♪ Into an ever-burning bright lamp light ♪

12:25.570 --> 12:28.240
♪ Live up to every year ♪

12:28.260 --> 12:31.490
♪ With fiery passion ♪

12:31.640 --> 12:34.420
♪ Even if I merge into ♪

12:34.440 --> 12:36.150
♪ The stream of stars in the end ♪

12:36.170 --> 12:38.440
♪ With thousands of li between us ♪

12:38.460 --> 12:44.480
♪ I never fade away within your eyes ♪

12:44.510 --> 12:47.170
♪ Gaze at endless streams and peaks ♪

12:47.190 --> 12:48.760
♪ Turn my whole heart ♪

12:48.780 --> 12:50.780
♪ Into the glimmering sun and moon ♪

12:50.810 --> 12:53.110
♪ Burn up every bit of time given ♪

12:53.130 --> 12:56.640
♪ Seek no karma nor any fruit ♪

12:56.880 --> 12:59.560
♪ Only one promise remains ♪

12:59.610 --> 13:01.420
♪ No time can tear us far apart ♪

13:01.440 --> 13:03.440
♪ It becomes an eternal old tale ♪

13:03.460 --> 13:05.920
♪ As mountains and seas change over time ♪

13:06.080 --> 13:10.200
♪ He keeps this memory close ♪

13:12.480 --> 13:16.240
♪ As long as the heart's light remains ♪

13:16.260 --> 13:25.730
♪ There won't be loneliness ♪

13:31.830 --> 13:33.110
I'm sorry.

13:33.140 --> 13:34.520
It's my fault for being so clumsy.

13:34.520 --> 13:36.380
I didn't take good care of Fan Yun.

13:37.140 --> 13:38.350
It's not your fault.

13:43.640 --> 13:45.700
Your Excellency, Lord Jiang is here.

13:46.080 --> 13:46.870
Send him in.

13:49.010 --> 13:50.090
Lord Jiang?

13:50.740 --> 13:52.930
The one who ranks first
on the Guanyu List

13:52.930 --> 13:54.680
but always wears a mask

13:54.750 --> 13:55.510
and never lets anyone

13:55.510 --> 13:57.100
see his true face.

13:57.610 --> 13:58.610
Since he is

13:58.670 --> 13:59.730
such a mysterious person,

13:59.730 --> 14:01.940
his medical skills must be extraordinary.

14:01.940 --> 14:04.010
It's said that those
who saw Lord Jiang's true face

14:04.010 --> 14:06.340
were almost scared to death by his beauty.

14:06.900 --> 14:09.200
Later, Lord Jiang
didn't want to cause trouble,

14:09.200 --> 14:10.510
nor did he want his beauty

14:10.510 --> 14:11.820
to overshadow his talent.

14:11.820 --> 14:12.570
So,

14:12.600 --> 14:14.000
he decided to wear a mask.

14:15.080 --> 14:16.480
I hope he can save Fan Yun.

14:18.130 --> 14:19.370
I also heard

14:19.400 --> 14:20.670
he's not only

14:20.690 --> 14:22.000
first on the Guanyu List

14:22.000 --> 14:23.800
but also first in the selection test
back then.

14:23.800 --> 14:26.380
He also has the best medical skills
in the Nine Cities.

14:26.380 --> 14:28.830
Lord Jiang Shu is exceptional
in both talent and looks.

14:28.830 --> 14:31.030
He definitely has a way to save Fan Yun.

14:31.060 --> 14:32.180
Your Excellency,

14:32.200 --> 14:33.120
Fan Yun

14:33.150 --> 14:34.750
will surely live a long life.

14:41.970 --> 14:43.630
Greetings, Your Excellency.

14:44.010 --> 14:46.760
[Jiang Shu, Manager
of the Commerce Ministry]

14:48.050 --> 14:48.840
Jiang Shu,

14:49.510 --> 14:50.750
what took you so long?

14:50.790 --> 14:51.630
Come,

14:51.630 --> 14:52.890
think of a way quickly.

14:53.760 --> 14:56.210
I will do my best.

14:56.230 --> 14:57.310
But...

14:57.690 --> 15:00.220
you and everyone,
please step outside first.

15:10.610 --> 15:12.610
I leave Fan Yun's life in your hands.

15:14.480 --> 15:15.440
Please.

15:30.850 --> 15:32.170
Your Excellency,

15:32.190 --> 15:34.070
can you stop pacing around?

15:34.100 --> 15:35.400
Didn't you say it yourself?

15:35.400 --> 15:36.470
Jiang Shu

15:36.500 --> 15:38.740
is the best doctor in the Nine Cities.

15:38.760 --> 15:39.880
It will be fine.

15:41.170 --> 15:41.890
Yes.

15:42.870 --> 15:45.100
But Jiang Shu has been handling
Commerce Ministry affairs.

15:45.100 --> 15:46.750
He hasn't practiced his medical skills.

15:46.750 --> 15:48.210
I don't know if he can do it.

15:49.060 --> 15:50.230
It'll be fine.

15:50.250 --> 15:51.770
Just relax.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.550
And you.

15:59.170 --> 15:59.630
He's out.

15:59.630 --> 16:00.760
Why isn't he out yet?

16:02.600 --> 16:03.360
Lord Jiang.

16:04.610 --> 16:05.280
Lord Jiang,

16:05.860 --> 16:06.690
how is Fan Yun?

16:09.370 --> 16:10.980
I can do nothing more.

16:13.030 --> 16:14.960
Her Ladyship is severely injured.

16:15.700 --> 16:16.890
I'm afraid...

16:19.340 --> 16:21.050
we can only leave it to fate.

16:21.080 --> 16:22.080
Lord Jiang,

16:22.100 --> 16:23.700
is there really no other way?

16:24.120 --> 16:25.050
Leave it to fate?

16:27.510 --> 16:28.860
What do you mean by that?

16:29.910 --> 16:31.310
There are no exceptions?

16:33.320 --> 16:34.510
Unless...

16:38.240 --> 16:39.670
Unless what?

16:41.270 --> 16:42.280
Say something!

16:43.310 --> 16:44.330
Unless what?

16:54.650 --> 16:56.650
We finally managed to escape this time

16:56.650 --> 16:58.080
and save our own lives.

16:58.100 --> 16:59.870
I didn't expect this person
to be so powerful,

16:59.870 --> 17:02.730
causing such heavy casualties
among our brothers.

17:03.990 --> 17:05.079
Don't mention it.

17:05.720 --> 17:07.800
Now we have meat and wine,

17:07.960 --> 17:09.349
which is pretty good.

17:09.790 --> 17:12.050
What exactly is the madam's background?

17:12.560 --> 17:15.880
They said the governor's wife
was as beautiful as a fairy,

17:15.960 --> 17:17.359
glamorous and charming.

17:17.950 --> 17:18.980
But when I saw her last time,

17:18.980 --> 17:20.430
she was just average.

17:20.480 --> 17:21.750
She's not even as pretty as the girls

17:21.750 --> 17:23.200
we find in the brothel.

17:23.540 --> 17:24.599
-Exactly.
-Right.

17:24.609 --> 17:26.329
-Come on.
-Drink up.

18:57.940 --> 18:59.940
You are from the Shadow Slay League?

19:16.430 --> 19:17.230
We

19:17.250 --> 19:19.250
don't cross paths with you.

19:19.280 --> 19:20.760
If you dare to touch us,

19:20.850 --> 19:22.000
the people behind us

19:22.080 --> 19:23.880
will never let you get away with it!

19:23.880 --> 19:25.370
What you just said

19:26.400 --> 19:27.770
made me very unhappy.

19:30.730 --> 19:33.160
Spare... spare me!

19:33.650 --> 19:34.900
Whenever we see you,

19:34.930 --> 19:36.660
we'll walk the other way, okay?

19:40.860 --> 19:43.380
Is Her Ladyship as beautiful as a fairy?

19:43.610 --> 19:45.180
Yes. Her Ladyship...

19:45.210 --> 19:46.650
Her Ladyship is as beautiful as a fairy!

19:46.650 --> 19:47.910
Absolutely stunning!

19:47.920 --> 19:49.370
A fairy from heaven!

19:54.230 --> 19:55.350
Send the people who hurt Her Ladyship

19:55.350 --> 19:57.150
in Linglong Tower that day here.

19:57.830 --> 19:58.460
Yes.

19:59.170 --> 20:00.460
Bring them up!

20:08.210 --> 20:09.010
That day,

20:09.040 --> 20:09.960
did you see Her Ladyship?

20:09.960 --> 20:11.130
I-I didn't see her.

20:11.150 --> 20:12.080
I didn't see her.

20:14.350 --> 20:15.550
Did you?

20:16.620 --> 20:17.970
I did! I did!

20:18.000 --> 20:18.890
I did!

20:23.490 --> 20:24.690
So it was you.

20:25.650 --> 20:26.280
It was me!

20:26.310 --> 20:27.910
It was me! It was me! It was me!

20:37.330 --> 20:39.790
Which hand did you use
to touch Her Ladyship?

20:42.130 --> 20:43.300
I... I...

20:43.330 --> 20:43.920
I didn't!

20:43.940 --> 20:44.900
I never touched her!

20:44.900 --> 20:45.690
I didn't!

20:48.450 --> 20:50.490
It wasn't me! I didn't touch her!

20:50.600 --> 20:51.560
It wasn't me!

20:58.710 --> 21:00.240
I asked you to think of a way.

21:00.400 --> 21:01.600
Why did you give me a history book?

21:01.600 --> 21:02.930
How do you explain this?

21:03.710 --> 21:04.670
The solution

21:04.690 --> 21:06.180
is in this history book.

21:10.050 --> 21:11.890
Before the late governor passed away,

21:11.890 --> 21:15.240
he used a specially provided
spiritual herb to prolong his life.

21:15.240 --> 21:16.610
It is said that this herb

21:16.630 --> 21:18.280
can repair muscles and bones,

21:18.280 --> 21:19.880
and neutralize all poisons.

21:20.570 --> 21:21.810
To save Her Ladyship,

21:22.950 --> 21:23.950
we have to find it.

21:24.480 --> 21:25.960
Then what are we waiting for?

21:25.960 --> 21:27.960
Hurry up and find this Bailing Herb.

21:30.880 --> 21:32.070
It's a pity.

21:33.050 --> 21:34.120
What's a pity?

21:35.550 --> 21:37.210
Can you finish your sentence?

21:38.790 --> 21:39.950
This herb is rare.

21:40.340 --> 21:42.230
After the late governor passed away,

21:42.230 --> 21:43.430
it has never appeared

21:43.850 --> 21:45.490
in the Nine Cities again.

21:49.150 --> 21:51.280
Are you messing with me on purpose?

21:52.590 --> 21:53.680
Don't wrong me.

21:54.170 --> 21:56.370
I hate being wronged the most in my life.

21:58.620 --> 22:00.080
Can you finish your words at once?

22:00.080 --> 22:01.540
I can't stand you anymore!

22:55.170 --> 22:56.300
Excuse me.

22:56.330 --> 22:58.590
Have you seen the Bailing Herb like this?

22:59.840 --> 23:00.800
No, I haven't.

23:07.810 --> 23:08.680
How is it?

23:10.260 --> 23:11.060
How about you?

23:58.660 --> 24:00.940
Roll in the good luck.

23:59.640 --> 24:02.780
♪ Watch how flowers bloom and wither ♪

24:01.800 --> 24:04.080
Roll away the villains.

24:03.200 --> 24:06.630
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

24:04.720 --> 24:07.240
Roll in the beneficiaries.

24:07.000 --> 24:09.560
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

24:08.110 --> 24:10.550
Roll away the diseases.

24:11.530 --> 24:14.450
Roll in good health.

24:15.620 --> 24:19.110
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

24:17.880 --> 24:18.960
I knew it.

24:19.670 --> 24:22.860
♪ Love cannot be cut away ♪

24:20.550 --> 24:22.510
How could such a silly method work?

24:23.610 --> 24:26.360
♪ How to let go? ♪

24:25.260 --> 24:26.950
If it were really good luck,

24:27.430 --> 24:29.490
why couldn't I find the Bailing Herb?

24:30.390 --> 24:31.560
Fan Yun,

24:31.580 --> 24:32.610
it's all my fault.

24:31.860 --> 24:35.210
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

24:34.960 --> 24:37.240
Although this trick successfully
lured out Zheng Yuan

24:35.550 --> 24:39.210
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

24:38.400 --> 24:39.780
and helped find the Dark Wolf,

24:39.780 --> 24:41.500
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

24:40.390 --> 24:42.000
it caused you to be like this.

24:41.910 --> 24:47.460
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

24:43.360 --> 24:44.560
It was my negligence.

24:45.730 --> 24:47.730
Bad luck, good luck,

24:47.750 --> 24:49.030
diseases, or health?

24:47.840 --> 24:49.330
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

24:49.370 --> 24:51.710
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

24:51.790 --> 24:53.110
Since my mother passed away

24:51.870 --> 24:55.040
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

24:53.830 --> 24:55.320
and Second Brother went missing,

24:55.320 --> 24:57.540
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

24:57.230 --> 24:58.550
in this world,

24:57.560 --> 24:59.930
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

24:58.600 --> 25:00.250
things I truly care about

24:59.960 --> 25:03.660
♪ Never mind fate dyes white crimson red ♪

25:01.610 --> 25:03.290
are very few indeed.

25:03.970 --> 25:05.310
♪ For whom does ♪

25:05.330 --> 25:07.500
♪ This phoenix blossom bloom? ♪

25:05.400 --> 25:07.010
The world scolds me

25:07.040 --> 25:07.710
and laughs at me,

25:07.530 --> 25:11.500
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

25:08.890 --> 25:09.820
so what?

25:11.600 --> 25:13.680
I will just play the fool

25:11.730 --> 25:13.780
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

25:13.710 --> 25:15.190
in front of them.

25:13.810 --> 25:16.200
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

25:16.520 --> 25:24.000
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

25:20.750 --> 25:22.350
But Fan Yun, do you know?

25:23.550 --> 25:24.750
I am

25:25.160 --> 25:27.020
destined to walk this path alone.

25:28.310 --> 25:30.470
But you appeared at this time

25:31.200 --> 25:32.880
and gave so much for me.

25:35.400 --> 25:36.480
Are you

25:38.680 --> 25:40.130
going to leave me now?

25:52.340 --> 25:56.520
♪ The wind arrives ♪

25:52.440 --> 25:55.000
Your Excellency, Your Excellency.

25:57.050 --> 25:57.980
Your Excellency,

25:57.980 --> 26:00.310
Lord Fan Qi heard that Her Ladyship
was seriously ill,

26:00.310 --> 26:02.040
so he specially sent this herb.

26:16.000 --> 26:17.030
The old rule.

26:18.480 --> 26:19.680
I eat the sesame,

26:19.800 --> 26:21.150
and you eat the pancake.

26:22.050 --> 26:23.050
Qiangwei,

26:23.630 --> 26:25.300
your spirit in heaven

26:25.350 --> 26:27.130
must bless our Yun.

26:27.400 --> 26:30.400
May heaven guard her, for good souls
receive divine protection.

26:30.400 --> 26:32.000
May she be blessed with peace

26:32.070 --> 26:33.350
and happiness.

26:48.040 --> 26:49.570
The Bailing Herb

26:49.600 --> 26:52.260
was exclusively supplied
to the late governor.

26:52.590 --> 26:54.340
Since the war 13 years ago,

26:54.640 --> 26:56.200
no one has seen it.

26:57.720 --> 26:59.850
You can give it a try, Your Excellency.

27:07.220 --> 27:09.710
You only came back
when there's the Bailing Herb.

27:09.710 --> 27:11.210
So should the credit go to you

27:11.210 --> 27:12.580
or the Bailing Herb?

27:13.750 --> 27:15.080
It is the will of Heaven.

27:15.700 --> 27:17.680
After Her Ladyship takes this medicine,

27:17.680 --> 27:19.510
she just needs to recuperate slowly.

27:19.510 --> 27:20.800
With some days of rest,

27:21.160 --> 27:23.420
her depleted vitality will be restored.

28:04.660 --> 28:05.280
Well...

28:10.830 --> 28:11.550
Well...

28:17.270 --> 28:18.030
All right.

28:20.350 --> 28:21.040
Come on.

29:35.000 --> 29:35.640
Well...

29:36.830 --> 29:37.490
Lord Jiang.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.840
Lord Jiang told me to do this.

29:40.640 --> 29:41.510
Lord Jiang.

29:42.200 --> 29:43.350
If it doesn't work,

29:43.390 --> 29:44.990
I will hold you accountable.

29:45.510 --> 29:46.510
Your Excellency,

29:46.790 --> 29:47.400
this is...

29:47.490 --> 29:48.770
I know. I know.

29:49.410 --> 29:50.410
You may leave now.

29:50.750 --> 29:52.680
Don't disturb her while she rests.

29:55.790 --> 29:56.990
I shall take my leave.

30:05.510 --> 30:06.400
Fan Yun.

30:21.070 --> 30:22.200
Miss Wei.

30:23.660 --> 30:25.190
Second Young Master Zheng.

30:25.940 --> 30:26.830
Miss Wei,

30:26.850 --> 30:28.550
are you heading
to Her Ladyship's chambers?

30:28.550 --> 30:29.880
Yes, I am on my way there.

30:30.020 --> 30:30.690
Why?

30:31.080 --> 30:32.770
Has the Zheng family moved
the Directorate of Education's classes

30:32.770 --> 30:34.370
to Her Ladyship's chambers?

30:35.330 --> 30:36.890
Now I know how eloquent

30:36.920 --> 30:38.380
and quick-witted you are.

30:38.540 --> 30:40.020
Hearing that Her Ladyship
is seriously ill,

30:40.020 --> 30:41.290
I gathered some medicinal herbs.

30:41.290 --> 30:42.690
I hope they can be of help.

30:42.730 --> 30:44.390
Please give them to her for me.

30:45.540 --> 30:46.260
No need.

30:46.290 --> 30:47.350
Fan Yun is fine now.

30:48.330 --> 30:49.910
Has Her Ladyship recovered?

30:49.910 --> 30:52.570
His Excellency found the Bailing Herb
for Fan Yun a few days ago.

30:52.570 --> 30:53.550
She has already taken it

30:53.550 --> 30:54.880
and is now recovering.

30:59.790 --> 31:01.200
But thank you anyway.

31:02.090 --> 31:03.090
Second Young Master Zheng,

31:03.090 --> 31:04.270
if there's nothing else,

31:04.270 --> 31:05.400
I will take my leave.

31:43.960 --> 31:44.960
Your Excellency,

31:45.480 --> 31:47.440
is Yun alright?

31:49.560 --> 31:51.160
She's taken the Bailing Herb

31:51.270 --> 31:52.530
and is getting better.

31:53.200 --> 31:54.270
Lord Fan Qi.

31:55.380 --> 31:56.110
No.

31:57.670 --> 32:00.130
I should call you Dark Wolf now,
shouldn't I?

32:00.550 --> 32:01.950
Do you still trust me now?

32:17.830 --> 32:18.900
I,

32:19.030 --> 32:20.110
naturally,

32:20.110 --> 32:22.000
trust you.

32:25.440 --> 32:27.570
Returning this to its rightful owner.

32:37.200 --> 32:38.400
Your Excellency,

32:38.400 --> 32:39.760
I

32:40.270 --> 32:42.240
really want to see

32:42.240 --> 32:44.480
our Nine Cities

32:44.620 --> 32:47.220
thrive in full prosperity,

32:48.680 --> 32:49.920
just like

32:51.520 --> 32:52.850
these phoenix flowers!

33:05.550 --> 33:06.310
Here.

33:06.650 --> 33:08.210
Slowly, it's hot.

33:11.730 --> 33:12.690
I heard

33:13.370 --> 33:15.480
this herb is extremely hard to find.

33:17.170 --> 33:19.700
Thank you for your trouble,
Your Excellency.

33:19.960 --> 33:21.140
Actually, this time,

33:21.140 --> 33:24.200
I wasn't the one who delivered
the medicine to save you.

33:24.240 --> 33:25.170
It was Dark Wolf.

33:27.120 --> 33:27.650
Well...

33:27.830 --> 33:28.830
Dark Wolf?

33:30.200 --> 33:33.240
Do you mean the one
hidden in the martial world,

33:33.240 --> 33:35.070
the terrifying Dark Wolf?

33:37.750 --> 33:38.750
Your Excellency,

33:39.030 --> 33:40.310
you found him?

33:42.750 --> 33:43.550
Oh, right.

33:45.070 --> 33:46.200
This

33:47.070 --> 33:48.680
was sent by Lord Fan Qi.

33:49.550 --> 33:51.600
He said you've hated bitter medicine
since you were little,

33:51.600 --> 33:54.130
so you must take it
with these candied fruits.

33:54.590 --> 33:56.030
He also said he made them himself.

33:56.030 --> 33:57.030
Have a taste.

33:59.230 --> 34:00.260
Father said

34:00.690 --> 34:02.340
he made these himself?

34:18.010 --> 34:20.010
What's wrong? Why are you laughing?

34:21.489 --> 34:24.020
He obviously bought these
at the corner shop.

34:24.070 --> 34:25.550
My father

34:25.550 --> 34:27.000
would blow up the kitchen

34:27.110 --> 34:28.630
just trying to boil an egg.

34:28.800 --> 34:30.400
How could he make these?

34:30.840 --> 34:32.170
I didn't expect Dark...

34:33.310 --> 34:35.770
Lord Fan Qi to be like this
behind the scenes.

34:39.840 --> 34:40.510
How is it?

34:41.110 --> 34:43.510
Do you feel better
after the candied fruit?

34:45.510 --> 34:46.280
Fan Yun.

34:48.190 --> 34:50.000
After going through this,

34:51.110 --> 34:53.110
I know your feelings for me are true.

34:54.560 --> 34:55.800
So from now on,

34:56.230 --> 34:57.630
I will treat you well.

35:01.760 --> 35:03.090
What's wrong? Choking?

35:03.390 --> 35:04.920
I'm fine, Your Excellency.

35:05.270 --> 35:05.830
Here.

35:09.880 --> 35:10.760
Y-Your Excellency,

35:10.760 --> 35:12.550
-Your Excellency, I can do it myself.
-It's fine.

35:12.550 --> 35:14.150
You are injured now.

35:14.150 --> 35:15.880
It is my duty to take care of you.

35:16.320 --> 35:16.850
I... I...

35:17.150 --> 35:19.070
Just give it to me.

35:19.070 --> 35:20.800
Don't worry, Your Excellency.

35:21.070 --> 35:23.110
I'm really fine now.

35:26.360 --> 35:27.190
That's good.

35:31.670 --> 35:32.360
Here.

35:33.800 --> 35:35.320
Hurry and drink the medicine.

35:35.320 --> 35:36.520
Don't let it get cold.

35:38.550 --> 35:39.110
Here.

35:39.670 --> 35:40.730
Careful, it's hot.

35:55.030 --> 35:55.920
What's wrong?
